response.overview: Six actors portray six personas of music legend Bob Dylan in scenes depicting various stages of his life, chronicling his rise from unknown folksinger to international icon and revealing how Dylan constantly reinvented himself.
response.tagline: All I can do is be me, whoever that is.
response.title: I'm Not There
